               stealing, on the <rs id="t18280911-238-cd1218" type="crimeDate">26th of July</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280911-238-off1217 t18280911-238-cd1218"></join>, 1 tea-kettle, value 3s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               <persName id="t18280911-238-victim1347" type="victimName">
                  John 
                  Bullock
               <interp inst="t18280911-238-victim1347" type="surname" value="Bullock"></interp>
